Global Emergency and Rescue Stretchers Market Insights
Emergency and Rescue Stretchers Market size was valued at USD 2.8 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Emergency and Rescue Stretchers Market Overview
The global Emergency and Rescue Stretchers market was valued at USD 3.5 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 5.9 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.3% from 2023 to 2030. This market growth is driven by the increasing demand for advanced and durable rescue equipment in emergency and disaster management. The market includes stretchers used for patient transportation, disaster relief, military and rescue operations, and more. Factors such as technological advancements in materials and the rising focus on healthcare and emergency services are expected to positively impact market growth.

